    summary: "Quockra-4 is a flat desert world with no rain, no oceans, and several extremely large salt flats. Dangerously hot at midday and very cold at night, its only city is built largely underground near the spaceport. The world appears to be populated entirely by droids of a thousand varieties — Imperial models and unknown alien designs — with yellow three-armed repair droids at the top, red worker droids in the middle, and Imperial droids at the bottom. What most visitors don't realize is that living creatures inhabit the planet: the Quockrans, enormous black-skinned slug-like beings who evolved when the planet was much more moist. They live deep underground, emerge only at night, and conduct all affairs through their droid servants to avoid alien contact. They are completely indifferent to galactic affairs and despise offworlders, though they are generally not violent about it.",
