    summary: "The Bpfassh system is a member of the New Republic, consisting of a double planet orbited by a complicated system of moons. The twin planets take the name of the star. Bpfassh was the target of a three-pronged Imperial attack shortly before the incident at Sluis Van — a setup for the real raid on the nearby Sluis Van Shipyards. Grand Admiral Thrawn attacked with a five-ship task force of Imperial Star Destroyers in a simple hit-and-fade tactic, striking Bpfassh and its two neighboring systems (both with names unpronounceable to humans) simultaneously. The Imperials attacked only to frighten and hurt, not to obliterate, hoping to force Bpfassh to call for help from Sluis Van — which would provide the Empire an opportunity to steal badly-needed starships. The planet and its moons were badly trashed, as were the neighboring systems, causing a lot of damage but surprisingly few deaths. A Republic-sponsored recovery program is currently underway.",
